 U7 ti-tu tiam3 ti7 chhiu7-na5 lai7, sek-ti3 kap ta e5 chhiu7-hioh8 saN-tang5; na7 hioh ti7 i e5 bang7--nih8, kha-chhiu2 khiu5-liu5--teh piN3 chhin-chhiuN7 hioh8. Koh chit8 ho7 e5 ti-tu, eng7 ta e5 chhiu7-hioh8 kap chhiN-thi5, lok ti7 bang7 e5 kiN-thau5, chiah bih ti7 hit lai7-bin7; lang5 boe7 hun-piat sim2-mih8 si7 hioh8, sim2-mih8 si7 ti-tu. 
