 Ti7 lam5-kek8 pak-kek8 loh8 seh kian peng ti3-kau3 si3-koe3 long2 peh8-peh8; hia e5 ia2-siu3, him5, chiau2, ah e5 sek-ti3 ia7 si7 peh8; lang5 beh liah8 a2-si7 phah-si2 hiah-e5 oah8-mih8 si7 oh-tit. Sai e5 sek-ti3 si7 ng5, kap i tiam3 e5 soa-sek piN5-piN5; sou2-i2 oe7 siam2-pi7 tui3-tek8. 
 Choa5 na7 tiam3 ti7 chhiu7-na5 a2-si7 thou5-khang, sek-ti3 khah toa7-bin7 si7 chhiN-sek, chhiah-sek; na7 soh ti7 chhiu7--nih8, lang5 khoaN3 choe3 chhiu7-ki, soa3 boe7 jin7-tit. Si3-kha choa5 ia7 si7 an2-ni, na7 un-lun-khun5 a2-si7 chhun tit8, chiu7 oe7 piN3-chiaN5 kap chhiu7-ki chhiu7-hioh8 a2-si7 chit8 in e5 chhau2 tang5-khoan2. Tui3 an2-ni oe7 siam2-pi7 tui3-tek8 lai5 po2-hou7 in e5 oah8-mia7. 
