 Thang5-thoa7 e5 lui7 chin gau5 siN-thoaN3, biat8 long2 boe7 liau2. Tak8 chiah hoe7 sou2 siN e5 nng7 pi2 50 chiah ke-bu2 sou2 siN-e5 khah choe7. Chit8 chiah ti-tu sou2 siN-chhut e5 ti-tu-kiaN2 sng3 boe7-tit liau2. Chit8 chiah phang-ong5 ti7 tu5-lai7 tak8 ni5 sou2 chhut e5 sin phang pi2 chit8 e5 toa7 siaN5 e5 peh-siN3 iau2 khah choe7. Oan-iuN siu7 e5 lai7-bin7 u7 oan-iuN-kiaN2 pi2 toa7 chang5 chhiu7 e5 hioh8 koh khah choe7. Hiah-e5 oah8-mih8 si7 khoai3 tu5 biat8-e5; chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 hou7 in gau5 siN-thoaN3; sui-bong2 tak8 jit8 lang5 ka7 phah-si2 choe7-choe7, iau2-ku2 sou2 chhun-e5 si7 chin choe7. 
